Is my bag packed?

816
01:07:59,538 --> 01:08:02,833
Mm-hm. Mine too.
What time do we leave?

817
01:08:03,000 --> 01:08:04,501
I have to leave right now.

818
01:08:04,710 --> 01:08:07,713
I'm going to Aberdeen to
supervise the interference project.

819
